					<description><![CDATA[I&#039;m a night person and I&#039;m a writer so I do this in reverse. A lot of days I don&#039;t touch email until 10am or 11am but it&#039;s always the first thing I do because I&#039;m still sluggish at that time. I get all the business aspect of writing finished during the day and when night comes my brain wakes up and I start writing. It&#039;s then that I ignore email and Facebook and the notifications that continually pop up. So this can work for us night owls as well.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I&#8217;m a night person and I&#8217;m a writer so I do this in reverse. A lot of days I don&#8217;t touch email until 10am or 11am but it&#8217;s always the first thing I do because I&#8217;m still sluggish at that time. I get all the business aspect of writing finished during the day and when night comes my brain wakes up and I start writing. It&#8217;s then that I ignore email and Facebook and the notifications that continually pop up. So this can work for us night owls as well.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
